__NOTOC__
{{Client function}}
{{New feature/item|3.0159|1.5.8|20854|This function clears the debug box.}}

==Syntax==
<syntaxhighlight lang="lua">
bool clearDebugBox ( )
</syntaxhighlight>

===Returns===
Always returns ''true''.

==Example==
This example clears the debug window when any new debug message is displayed.
<syntaxhighlight lang="lua">
addEventHandler ( "onClientDebugMessage", root,
	function ( )
		clearDebugBox ( )
	end
)
</syntaxhighlight>

==Requirements==
{{Requirements|n/a|1.5.8-9.20854|}}

